title: $:/plugins/tiddlywiki/palettes-2026/readme

This plugin contains thirty three colour palettes adapted from the [[yatagarasu|https://yatagarasu.tiddlyhost.com/]] collection by [[spoon-cat|https://spoon-cat.tiddlyhost.com]], with thanks.

The palettes are built on palette inheritance: each palette imports the shared base palette `$:/palettes/2026/base` and defines ten base colours, from which the base palette derives the full set of palette entries. When one of these palettes is selected, a settings panel appears beneath the palette chooser with a colour picker for each base colour.

Palette authors can import `$:/palettes/2026/base` in their own palettes to use the same mechanism.
